data.description: This is a move in condition home located just out of town. This is a stick built home. Enjoy the comforts of country living with well and public sewer. This home has large kitchen with island and an eat in area. Appliances are stainless steel and will remain. Plenty of granite counter tops. Great storage for all your cooking needs. Great room with plenty of windows to bring in natural light. Gas fireplace with blower and controlled by thermostat. Family room with built in desk area for office use if needed. Pellet stove could be used for additional heat if needed. Master bedroom does have wall to wall carpeting and two large closets. Master bath has double sinks, updated tiled shower. After a long day, you may want to enjoy the whirlpool tub. The second and third bedrooms both have wall to wall carpeting and large closets. Enjoy the wildlife from rear deck. Sit on front porch and enjoy the view! The storage shed does have electric to it. Don't miss out on this home or location.
